windup:xpath-value.description:
When using CXF, the WebSphere built-in JAX-WS engine needs to be disabled. Use the following snippet:
                        <code>
                        &lt;plugin&gt;
                            &lt;artifactId&gt;maven-war-plugin&lt;/artifactId&gt;
                            &lt;configuration&gt;
                                &lt;archive&gt;
                                    &lt;manifestEntries&gt;
                                        &lt;DisableIBMJAXWSEngine&gt;true&lt;/DisableIBMJAXWSEngine&gt;
                                    &lt;/manifestEntries&gt;
                                &lt;/archive&gt;
                            &lt;/configuration&gt;
                        &lt;/plugin&gt;
                        </code>
